{"tid":1617171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香城online] 結界師學徒~和理非都可以!","createTime":"2019-10-03T16:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T18:05:43.000Z","uid":211634,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8504c5472717befa3e4bd5a3c2b05cb8bf7506e0","tid":1617171,"uid":211634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:24:21.000Z","msg":"大家都知道依排新職結界師好受歡迎, 你係咪都想加入? 但自己又和理非, 又怕怕, 咁零風險呢?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁做個結界師學徒啦!</span><br />\n<br />\n隨身一兩把鎖頭, bluetap或者香口膠, 隱身裝備<br />\n時間緊係落晒閘鎖左後<br />\n對生怪點, 運怪出口, 或者又紅又藍既店, 幫佢落個結界<br />\n人地有鎖既, 用bluetap/香口膠塞左佢, 令佢想開番都冇得開, 要爆鎖, 總之有窿就塞死佢<br />\n佢冇鎖頭既, 睇下有冇位可以用鎖頭卡死門/閘, 同樣要填番D窿窿<br />\n<br />\n進一步:<br />\n單車鎖, 20蚊左右就夠, 消耗品唔好太貴, 咁多數左右開既閘都OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n電閘既話, 未研究, 不過電係怕水既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作用: 第2朝一開門發現開唔到, 搵開鎖佬都要時間, 咁早應該好難搵, 搵到都好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n減少營業時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係生怪位, 可能要多D風險, 自己衡量, 不過會有多D作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住自己只係學徒, 失敗冇作用係常事, 只要人冇事, 大把目標比你練習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最最最重要, 記得著隱身裝"},{"pid":"851f82c785db269bea91044a82e3f40b1a3d3496","tid":1617171,"uid":167758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:25:45.000Z","msg":"721811831929101"},{"pid":"8741155955b0817273721d78cd0f667a21d70fac","tid":1617171,"uid":115410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8504c5472717befa3e4bd5a3c2b05cb8bf7506e0","tid":1617171,"uid":211634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:24:21.000Z","msg":"大家都知道依排新職結界師好受歡迎, 你係咪都想加入? 但自己又和理非, 又怕怕, 咁零風險呢?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁做個結界師學徒啦!</span><br />\n<br />\n隨身一兩把鎖頭, bluetap或者香口膠, 隱身裝備<br />\n時間緊係落晒閘鎖左後<br />\n對生怪點, 運怪出口, 或者又紅又藍既店, 幫佢落個結界<br />\n人地有鎖既, 用bluetap/香口膠塞左佢, 令佢想開番都冇得開, 要爆鎖, 總之有窿就塞死佢<br />\n佢冇鎖頭既, 睇下有冇位可以用鎖頭卡死門/閘, 同樣要填番D窿窿<br />\n<br />\n進一步:<br />\n單車鎖, 20蚊左右就夠, 消耗品唔好太貴, 咁多數左右開既閘都OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n電閘既話, 未研究, 不過電係怕水既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作用: 第2朝一開門發現開唔到, 搵開鎖佬都要時間, 咁早應該好難搵, 搵到都好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n減少營業時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係生怪位, 可能要多D風險, 自己衡量, 不過會有多D作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住自己只係學徒, 失敗冇作用係常事, 只要人冇事, 大把目標比你練習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最最最重要, 記得著隱身裝"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:27:51.000Z","msg":"唔好香口膠得唔得，咬完有證據喎"},{"pid":"ee0cf7a415c87fe0166a5783047fa94dbcd47279","tid":1617171,"uid":211634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8741155955b0817273721d78cd0f667a21d70fac","tid":1617171,"uid":115410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8504c5472717befa3e4bd5a3c2b05cb8bf7506e0","tid":1617171,"uid":211634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:24:21.000Z","msg":"大家都知道依排新職結界師好受歡迎, 你係咪都想加入? 但自己又和理非, 又怕怕, 咁零風險呢?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁做個結界師學徒啦!</span><br />\n<br />\n隨身一兩把鎖頭, bluetap或者香口膠, 隱身裝備<br />\n時間緊係落晒閘鎖左後<br />\n對生怪點, 運怪出口, 或者又紅又藍既店, 幫佢落個結界<br />\n人地有鎖既, 用bluetap/香口膠塞左佢, 令佢想開番都冇得開, 要爆鎖, 總之有窿就塞死佢<br />\n佢冇鎖頭既, 睇下有冇位可以用鎖頭卡死門/閘, 同樣要填番D窿窿<br />\n<br />\n進一步:<br />\n單車鎖, 20蚊左右就夠, 消耗品唔好太貴, 咁多數左右開既閘都OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n電閘既話, 未研究, 不過電係怕水既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作用: 第2朝一開門發現開唔到, 搵開鎖佬都要時間, 咁早應該好難搵, 搵到都好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n減少營業時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係生怪位, 可能要多D風險, 自己衡量, 不過會有多D作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住自己只係學徒, 失敗冇作用係常事, 只要人冇事, 大把目標比你練習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最最最重要, 記得著隱身裝"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:27:51.000Z","msg":"唔好香口膠得唔得，咬完有證據喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:29:14.000Z","msg":"係WO, 你啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎大家比意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d170d8dd50135f6ceabca242fe5607d693f90f","tid":1617171,"uid":299623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:29:24.000Z","msg":"小心封印到自己人 要小心用"},{"pid":"7ad509a37197931252d730505bae3c8a987b5ad1","tid":1617171,"uid":33851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:37:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b488756f9da6ae0e5b9ac1ed02c7b5625ae0e7","tid":1617171,"uid":211634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:41:56.000Z","msg":"建議大家帶幾支牙簽, 咁D料就好易入晒個窿窿喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525ea4a3a1fe22a4be9e3af1293955583162f5ae","tid":1617171,"uid":306434,"like":